# UI Design System

## Color Palette

### Primary Colors
- **Pure Black**: `#000000` - Main text, headers, primary actions
- **Pure White**: `#FFFFFF` - Backgrounds, cards, secondary text

### Accent Colors
- **Champagne Gold**: `#D4AF37` - Premium touches, highlights, CTAs
- **Premium Blue**: `#1E3A8A` - Status indicators, alerts, secondary actions

### Neutral Grays
Use Tailwind CSS gray scale: `gray-50`, `gray-100`, `gray-200`, `gray-300`, `gray-400`, `gray-500`, `gray-600`, `gray-700`, `gray-800`, `gray-900`

### Status Colors
- **Success Green**: `#059669` - Success states, confirmations
- **Warning Amber**: `#D97706` - Warnings, pending states
- **Error Red**: `#DC2626` - Errors, destructive actions

## Typography

### Font Families
- **Headers**: SF Pro Display / Poppins (Bold, SemiBold)
- **Body**: SF Pro Text / Inter (Regular, Medium)

### Font Hierarchy
- **H1**: 32px (2rem) - Main page titles
- **H2**: 24px (1.5rem) - Section headers
- **H3**: 18px (1.125rem) - Subsection headers
- **Body**: 16px (1rem) - Main content text
- **Caption**: 14px (0.875rem) - Secondary text, labels

## Design Principles

### Spacing
- **Minimum padding**: 16px (1rem) for all containers
- **Generous white space**: Use consistent spacing scale
- **Component spacing**: 8px, 16px, 24px, 32px, 48px increments

### Visual Effects
- **Shadows**: Subtle elevation with `shadow-sm`, `shadow-md`, `shadow-lg`
- **Transitions**: 300ms ease-in-out for all interactive elements
- **Border radius**: Consistent 8px for cards, 4px for buttons

### Icons & Illustrations
- **Icon style**: Minimalist line icons
- **Illustrations**: Subtle, clean illustrations
- **Icon size**: 16px, 20px, 24px for different contexts

### Loading States
- **Skeleton loaders**: Required for all async content
- **Loading animations**: Smooth, subtle transitions
- **Empty states**: Clear messaging with appropriate illustrations

## Implementation Guidelines

### CSS Classes
```css
/* Typography */
.text-h1 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; }
.text-h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; }
.text-h3 { font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; }
.text-body { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 400; }
.text-caption { font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400; }

/* Transitions */
.transition-smooth { transition: all 300ms ease-in-out; }
```

